      Call LECTEXTRA([M:PJTAC0A]WSTDES, "WORKSTATIO", "WSTDESAXX", VALEUR, [M:PJTAC0]TASFCY) From ATEXTRA    # Issue X3-99916 - 2018-07-12 by FGR : not [M:PJTAC0] from now
